in the Ye family's backyard.

21
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:11,120
I remember once,

22
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:12,870
we even burned the lawn.

23
00:01:13,710 --> 00:01:14,550
Yes, indeed.

24
00:01:14,920 --> 00:01:15,920
At that time,

25
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,400
you were so scared
that hid in Mom's arms,

26
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:18,640
crying loudly

27
00:01:19,070 --> 00:01:21,000
and clutching her jade bracelet.

28
00:01:21,790 --> 00:01:22,710
She had no choice,

29
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,280
so she searched through

30
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:26,230
the pile of sweet potatoes

31
00:01:26,710 --> 00:01:27,680
and coaxed you

32
00:01:27,710 --> 00:01:29,040
to find you the sweetest one

33
00:01:29,230 --> 00:01:31,150
in the world.

34
00:01:35,920 --> 00:01:36,950
It was really sweet.

35
00:01:38,430 --> 00:01:39,280
Honestly,

36
00:01:39,310 --> 00:01:40,710
