42
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:55,950
from the Ye family.

43
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:57,920
It doesn't matter.

44
00:01:58,510 --> 00:01:59,480
From the moment I heard

45
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:01,310
you'd returned to Chongjiang,

46
00:02:01,510 --> 00:02:03,840
